data.title: Kelly Johnson, LCSW
data.meta_description: Kelly Johnson was born in Brooklyn, NY and raised in Ithaca. With 20 years of experience, presenting issues in her work include but are not limited to anxiety, depression, relationship issues, grief and loss, and trauma. Kelly believes in exploring inner strength, empowerment, and self-advocacy to guide you through your journey to achieve balance and fulfillment.
data.text: If you or someone you know is experiencing an emergency or crisis and needs immediate help, call 911 or go to the nearest emergency room. Additional crisis resources can be found here.
